description:
Aviation Week Network is proud to announce that the Asia Aerospace Leadership Forum & MRO Asia-Pacific Awards Dinner will take place on 19 September 2022 in Singapore, in conjunction with MRO Asia-Pacific.
    
    With the burgeoning demand for air travel coming as a relief to the industry, we are now at a fascinating inflection point in recent aviation history. Aftermarket demand is regaining momentum, sweeping technological and operational revolutions are at various points of their lifecycles, and new sustainability initiatives are becoming more important than ever. 
    
    The pivot to a "new normal" will differ sector-by-sector, and is complicated not only by the shadow of COVID-19 but also rapidly shifting trading patterns and alliances resulting from Russia’s military action in Ukraine.
    
    This unique hybrid event will provide a platform for regional aerospace and aviation leadership to share their latest thinking on state of the market, before going on to celebrate the
title: Asia Aerospace Leadership Forum & MRO Asia-Pacific Awards
